INPUTS
--------------------
input_file             File that contains the list of edges (.pairs or .wpairs)
clustering_file        File that contains the list of node-community pairs (.graph)

RUNNING
--------------------
To compile:

	$ javac MetricScoreCalculator.java

To Run:

	$ java MetricScoreCalculator input_file clustering_file

TEST RUN
--------------------

Terminal input:

	$ javac MetricScoreCalculator.java
	$ java MetricScoreCalculator ~/Downloads/ground-truth/karate/karate.pairs ~/Downloads/ground-truth/karate/karate-lm-silhouette.graph 

Terminal output:

	-------------------------------------
	Metric Score Calculator
	-------------------------------------
	coverage:   0.717948717948718
	modularity: 0.2790927021696252
	silhouette: 0.023668630613909947

